{"tid":2322032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大媽跳老舞唔罰]限聚令罰款提高至 5000 元首日　警票控十多名「鳩嗚團」成員違令","createTime":"2020-12-12T04:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T04:23:24.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ddcb2fe2b4640ce46ca2c53fd91750e15aa350","tid":2322032,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/5000%E5%85%83%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5-%E8%AD%A6%E7%A5%A8%E6%8E%A710%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%B3%A9%E5%97%9A%E5%9C%98-%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F5000%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%258E%25A710%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%25B3%25A9%25E5%2597%259A%25E5%259C%2598-%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=cd449f20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F5000%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%258E%25A710%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%25B3%25A9%25E5%2597%259A%25E5%259C%2598-%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&h=3434e7e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/5000%E5%85%83%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5-%E8%AD%A6%E7%A5%A8%E6%8E%A710%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%B3%A9%E5%97%9A%E5%9C%98-%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4/</a><br />\n<br />\n限聚令提高罰款第一日，警方昨晚 (11 日) 在旺角向十多名「旺角鳩嗚團」成員發出定額罰款通知書，指他們涉嫌違反《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集）規例》(599G)。油尖旺區區議員朱江瑋指，他昨晚在現場觀察所見，亞皆老街附近同時有一批人士聚集唱歌，又有人沒有正確配戴口罩，質疑警方選擇性執法。<br />\n<br />\n政府提高違反限聚令的定額罰款，由 2,000 元增至 5,000 元，昨天是生效第一日。多名「旺角鳩嗚團」成員被警方票控違反限聚令，至少 16 人遭票控，有一名算命師傅指自己路過亦被票控，認為「警察大晒，警察不能冤枉人，罷明屈人。」<br />\n<br />\n另有二人被帶返警署，朱江瑋指其中一人因沒有帶身份證，帶到警署半小時內已被釋放；另一人則涉及欠交法庭傳票，故仍在警署。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">朱江瑋指他當時在附近有活動，收到消息馬上趕到現場，同時發現亞皆老街有「大媽唱歌團開到鬼死咁大聲」，但警方卻沒有行動，認為「擺明針對，有意打壓」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2014 年雨傘運動後期，警方於旺角執行禁制令清除佔領區後，有市民繼續以「鳩嗚」名義於附近一帶聚集，高呼「我要鳩嗚」(與「購物」的普通話音相近)。至今仍有一批中年人士堅持「鳩嗚團」精神，每晚於西洋菜街擺檔宣揚真普選。今年 9 月 6 日「九龍遊行」後，警方亦曾以違反限聚令為由，在旺角票控約十名「鳩嗚團」成員。<br />\n<br />\n    名鳩嗚團友被抄5️⃣9️⃣9️⃣G❗❗總共有14人被抄5️⃣9️⃣9️⃣G❗有兩位伯伯被帶上警車❗其中一位伯伯冇帶身份證❗❗<br />\n    由旺角《鳩嗚團》by《MK Mickey》發佈於 2020年12月11日 星期五"},{"pid":"c450583d714b84e64cdab3ae3054c019efa384cd","tid":2322032,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲都拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551fe92d081fe401159f3588edc5e6334a951797","tid":2322032,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c450583d714b84e64cdab3ae3054c019efa384cd","tid":2322032,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲都拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"防疫做籍口，實情係政治打壓"},{"pid":"d559cfb7e8cd71431d9862415d340bf255245f57","tid":2322032,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"啊sir要叫雞<br />\n拉左點屌西"},{"pid":"14dc0ffbabb64d0418081d6d02be6c57d60cc629","tid":2322032,"uid"